resources.name: Prevent the aircraft from moving based on the queue
Resume aircraft movement based on the queue
Returns the current list of waypoints in the queue
Overwrite the queue with a new list of waypoints

resources.contents:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: "This is the API that the MissionPlanner Scripts server exposes to GCOM."
  version: 0.0.1
  title: MissionPlanner Scripts
tags:
  - name: queue
    description: Access to aicraft waypoint queue
  - name: status
    description: Current aircraft status
  - name: lock
    description: Toggle queue-based movement
paths:
  /queue:
    get:
      tags:
        - queue
      summary: Returns the current list of waypoints in the queue
      description: ""
      operationId: getQueue
      responses:
        "200":
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Waypoint"
    post: 
      tags:
        - queue
      summary: Overwrite the queue with a new list of waypoints 
      description: Altitude can be null
      operationId: updateQueue
      requestBody:
        $ref: "#/components/requestBodies/Queue"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: successful operation
        "400":
          description: bad request
  /status:
    get:
      tags:
        - status
      summary: Obtain the aircraft status
      description: ""
      operationId: status
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Status"
  /lock:
    get:
      tags:
        - lock
      summary: Prevent the aircraft from moving based on the queue
      description: ""
      operationId: lock
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
        "400":
          description: Aircraft already locked or queue empty
  /unlock:
    get:
      tags:
        - lock
      summary: Resume aircraft movement based on the queue
      description: ""
      operationId: unlock
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
        "400":
          description: Aircraft already unlocked
components:
  requestBodies:
    Queue:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Queue"
      description: Queue of waypoints
      required: true
  schemas:
    Queue:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Waypoint"
    Waypoint:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        longitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
        latitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
        altitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
      xml:
        name: Queue
    Status:
      type: object
      properties:
        velocity:
          type: number
          format: float64
        longitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
        latitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
        altitude:
          type: number
          format: float64
        heading:
          type: number
          format: float64
      xml:
        name: Status
